6. Add human-in-the-loop override

This is a killer feature.

After the model recommends ESI-2, show:

Nurse decision: Accept / Override
Override reason: “Patient looks stable” / “Concern for deterioration” / free text
Save to audit log

Then build a dashboard:

Model agreed with nurse: 72%
Nurse upgraded acuity: 18%
Nurse downgraded acuity: 10%
Most common override reason: abnormal appearance / clinical concern

This turns your app from “AI gives answer” into “AI supports clinical workflow,” which is much more credible.

